Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/bobgreenshields/dotfiles.git

or if you are likely to be editing
    git clone git@github.com:bobgreenshields/dotfiles.git

After chef install use

    git remote set-url origin git@github.com:bobgreenshields/dotfiles.git

to switch from https to ssh

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/bashrc ~/.bashrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/pentadactylrc ~/.pentadactylrc

Switch to the `~/dotfiles` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/dotfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
